## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **gefapixant Lyfnua (EU 2023) + Lyfagra (한국 2024 KFDA) + FDA 2024** = first FDA P2X3 antagonist refractory chronic cough — paradigm shift. COUGH-1 + COUGH-2 Phase 3 data 후 FDA 2024 approval. taste-loss (P2X2/3 hetero) 부작용 ~58% 가 limiting factor. 양자-VQE 의 P2X3 selectivity vs P2X2/3 hetero 가 직접 fit.
2. **camlipixant (BLU-5937, Bellus → GSK 인수) Phase 3** = second-gen P2X3 selective — taste-loss 회피가 design goal. P2X3 vs P2X2/3 hetero selectivity ratio 가 gefapixant 보다 높음. 양자-VQE 의 P2X3 homotrimer pocket selectivity 가 fit.
3. **sivopixant (Shionogi) Phase 3** = third P2X3 selective — Japan-led. 한국/일본 RCC 임상 paradigm 의 next entry. 양자-VQE 의 P2X3 selectivity 가 cross-asia.
4. **eliapixant (Bayer) Phase 2 fail 2022** = P2X3 selective discontinued — efficacy issue. P2X3 class drug development 의 falsifier 중요 사례. 양자-VQE 의 binding affinity vs functional efficacy 의 분리 modeling 한정.
5. **orvepitant (NeRRe) Phase 2 chronic cough** = NK1 antagonist — substance P/NK1 axis 가 P2X3 가 아닌 alternative target. 양자-VQE 의 NK1 receptor pocket 가 fit (cross-bipolar_disorder + ptsd_anxiety nonscope).
6. **codeine + dextromethorphan + 만성 OTC opioid** = 만성 historical antitussive — 만성 abuse + dependency 한계. 만성 opioid axis 가 P2X3-class 의 displacement target. 양자-VQE 의 μ-opioid + sigma1 receptor pocket 가 cross-substance_use 한정.
7. **gabapentin + pregabalin + amitriptyline + tramadol + baclofen 만성 off-label** = 만성 chronic cough 의 neurogenic paradigm. α2δ + TCA + GABA-B + opioid weak/SNRI 의 다축 mechanism. 양자-VQE 의 α2δ pocket 가 fit (cross-chronic_neuropathic_pain_specific).
8. **ICS + LABA + LAMA + LTRA** = 만성 cough-variant asthma cross-asthma_specific. PCAB + alginate + PPI = 만성 GERD-related cough cross-gerd_pud_specific. INS + azelastine + 2nd-gen H1 = 만성 UACS cross-otolaryngology + allergy_immunodef. ACE-i induced cough → ARB switch = mechanism-driven displacement. 양자-VQE 의 5-source chronic cough mechanism heterogeneous pocket 가 fit.
9. **K-cough + 식약처 framework + 한국 한의학 cough remedy + Lyfagra 2024 KFDA** = 한국 K-pharma industry chronic cough 표적 의 글로벌 paradigm 시제품. 본 양자-VQE 가 한국-IP novel candidate (hxq-cough-p2x3-001) 에 직접 fit (cross-K_pharma_industry).
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, chronic cough + RCC + UACS + ACE-i induced 임상 의미 한정. 만성 long-term safety + 만성 taste-loss + 만성 placebo response (~40% RCC trials) = 임상 RCT 가 결정.

